OL,3,CGeorge Carey facing possible
OL,4,Cdisciplinary action after abuse report
OL,6,FFormer archbishop of Canterbury George
OL,7,FCarey is among a number of clergy
OL,8,Ffacing possible disciplinary action
OL,9,Fafter a damning abuse report which
OL,10,Fprompted Justin Welby's resignation.
OL,12,FLord Carey was named in the Makin
OL,13,Freview, which concluded abuse carried
OL,14,Fout for decades by Christian camp
OL,15,Fleader John Smyth was known about and
OL,16,Fnot acted upon by various people
OL,17,Fwithin the Church.
