OL,3,CGeorge Carey facing possible
OL,4,Cdisciplinary action after abuse report
OL,6,FLord Carey resigned as a priest in
OL,7,FDecember following an investigation
OL,8,Finto the Church of England's handling
OL,9,Fof a separate sexual abuse case.
OL,11,FHe is one of 10 clergy named by the
OL,12,FChurch's national safeguarding team
OL,13,F(NST) on Tuesday as people they are
OL,14,Fseeking to bring disciplinary
OL,15,Fproceedings against over potential
OL,16,Ffailures in safeguarding.
OL,18,FThe Makin report said Lord Carey had
OL,19,Fbeen informed of Smyth's abuse and
OL,20,Fbeen sent a copy of a previous report
OL,21,Finto it "but he denies seeing it".
