OL,6,FThe others named include Reverend Sue
OL,7,FColman, who is the wife of the
OL,8,FColman's mustard heir Sir Jamie Colman.
OL,10,FThe Makin report concluded Mrs Colman,
OL,11,Fassociate minister at St Leonard's
OL,12,FChurch in Oakley, near Basingstoke in
OL,13,FHampshire, was aware of Smyth's abuse
OL,14,Fbefore being ordained and noted that
OL,15,Fshe and her husband visited Smyth in
OL,16,FAfrica in the 1990s and funded the
OL,17,FSmyths through a personal trust.
