OL,6,FThe others name by the NST are Bishop
OL,7,FPaul Butler, Reverend Roger Combes,
OL,8,FReverend Andrew Cornes, Reverend Tim
OL,9,FHastie-Smith, Reverend Hugh Palmer,
OL,10,FReverend Paul Perkin, Reverend Nick
OL,11,FStott and Reverend John Woolmer.
OL,13,FThe NST said in all cases it would be
OL,14,Fasking for permission of the President
OL,15,Fof the Tribunals to bring a clergy
OL,16,Fdiscipline measure (CDM) "out of time"
OL,17,F` as currently there is a 12-month
OL,18,Ftime limit on cases being brought.
