OL,3,CGeorge Carey facing possible
OL,4,Cdisciplinary action after abuse report
OL,6,FThe independent review by Keith Makin
OL,7,Finto the Church of England's handling
OL,8,Fof allegations of serious abuse by
OL,9,FSmyth was published in November and
OL,10,Fled to the eventual resignation of Mr
OL,11,FWelby as archbishop of Canterbury.
OL,13,FThe review concluded that barrister
OL,14,FSmyth, thought to be the most prolific
OL,15,Fserial abuser to be associated with
OL,16,Fthe Church, might have been brought to
OL,17,Fjustice had Mr Welby formally reported
OL,18,Fallegations to police in 2013.
