OL,3,CGeorge Carey facing possible
OL,4,Cdisciplinary action after abuse report
OL,6,FSmyth is said to have subjected his
OL,7,Fvictims to traumatic attacks across
OL,8,Ffive decades in three different
OL,9,Fcountries and involving as many as 130
OL,10,Fboys and young men in the UK and
OL,11,FAfrica.
OL,13,FHe died aged 77 in Cape Town in 2018
OL,14,Fwhile under investigation by Hampshire
OL,15,FPolice, and so was "never bought to
OL,16,Fjustice for the abuse".
