OL,3,CGeorge Carey facing possible
OL,4,Cdisciplinary action after abuse report
OL,6,FAlexander Kubeyinje, the Church of
OL,7,FEngland's national director of
OL,8,Fsafeguarding, said: "We must not
OL,9,Fforget that at heart of this case are
OL,10,Fthe survivors and victims who have
OL,11,Fendured the lifelong effects of the
OL,12,Fappalling abuse by John Smyth, we are
OL,13,Ftruly sorry.
OL,15,F"Today we have announced next steps in
OL,16,Fthe process looking at both risk and
OL,17,Fdisciplinary processes.
